     7	## Quick start
     8	
     9	```bash
    10	# 1. Start the FastAPI backend in another shell (loopback only):
    11	uvicorn ui.backend.main:app --host 127.0.0.1 --port 8000 --reload
    12	
    13	# 2. Install + run the dev server:
