    21	in Phase 0. Port 5180 (not the Vite default 5173) is deliberate — see
    22	`ui/frontend/vite.config.ts` rationale for why. Override via
    23	`npm run dev -- --port NNNN` or `CFD_FRONTEND_PORT=NNNN ./scripts/start-ui-dev.sh`.
