+- R1-M3 [verify]: addressed in `6911611` — the home-page CTA strip now includes GitHub, `/pro`, and a mailto inquiry path (`ui/frontend/src/pages/learn/LearnHomePage.tsx:82-117`).
+- R1-M4 [verify]: addressed in `6911611` — the three-strip differentiation band now names real-solver evidence, literature-backed comparator, and signed audit package explicitly (`ui/frontend/src/pages/learn/LearnHomePage.tsx:57-79`).
+- R1-M5 [verify]: addressed in `6911611` — the placeholder-alert nav items are gone; the top nav only exposes real `/learn` and `/pro` routes (`ui/frontend/src/components/learn/LearnLayout.tsx:22-47`).
+- R1-N1 [verify]: addressed in `6911611` — the left-rail tagline is now buyer-readable and the internal Path-B provenance moved to the footer (`ui/frontend/src/components/Layout.tsx:43-49`, `ui/frontend/src/components/Layout.tsx:90-93`).
+- New findings:
