+- R2-M3 [verify]: addressed in `6911611` — plane-channel mesh labels are now honest cell counts (`20³/40³/80³/160³`) and the in-file comment explicitly says the old `WR-LES` / `DNS` labels overstated the solver path (`ui/frontend/src/pages/learn/LearnCaseDetailPage.tsx:98-112`).
+- R2-M4 [verify]: addressed in `6c53986` — impinging_jet now frames A4 as the observable symptom, names the root cause as composite, and defers root-cause audit to Phase 9 rather than pretending one knob fix exists (`knowledge/gold_standards/impinging_jet.yaml:15-18`, `knowledge/gold_standards/impinging_jet.yaml:27-28`).
